OL,3,CBusiness owner frustrated at city's
OL,4,C'Glory Hole' footway closure
OL,6,FA business owner in is calling for
OL,7,Fquicker action following the closure
OL,8,Fof the city's 'Glory Hole' walkway.
OL,10,FThere was a partial collapse of the
OL,11,Ffootway between Wigwford Way and the
OL,12,FHigh Street in February 2023 which
OL,13,Fresulted in closing it for temporary
OL,14,Frepairs. Further investigations found
OL,15,Fthere was more damage and extra works
OL,16,Fwould be required.
OL,18,FRoger Baldam-Lucas, owner of the Now
OL,19,FHair by the Glory Hole footway, said
OL,20,Fhe has had to move to a temporary
OL,21,Flocation.
