OL,3,CBusiness owner frustrated at city's
OL,4,C'Glory Hole' footway closure
OL,6,F"It is a huge inconvenience", he said.
OL,8,F"We had to shut this down and let our
OL,9,Fcustomer base know and redirect
OL,10,Fbecause they couldn't come through
OL,11,Fhere. We've not got any passing trade
OL,12,Fwhich has impacted our footfall.
OL,14,F"Costs are going up constantly with
OL,15,Fthe business and if there is no money
OL,16,Fcoming in then we'll have to close our
OL,17,Fdoors."
OL,19,FLincolnshire County Council say there
OL,20,Fneeds to be more extensive work before
OL,21,Fthe footway can reopen.
