OL,3,CBusiness owner frustrated at city's
OL,4,C'Glory Hole' footway closure
OL,6,F"We've recently made preparations on-
OL,7,Fsite, including removing slabs,
OL,8,Fconcrete fill and rotten timbers, and
OL,9,Fare mobilising a floating pontoon so
OL,10,Fwe can safely rebuild Glory Hole.
OL,11,FHowever, we are subject to
OL,12,Frestrictions on the River Witham
OL,13,Fregarding fast flowing water following
OL,14,Fthe recent inclement weather. Only
OL,15,Fthen will we be ready to start the
OL,16,Frepairs, which could take up to five
OL,17,Fweeks.
OL,19,F"Until it's fully repaired, the
OL,20,Fcurrent pedestrian diversion will
OL,21,Fremain in place at the Glory Hole."
